IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. CALCULATOR.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  WS-COUNT        PIC S9(9).
01  WS-REMAINDER    PIC S9(9).
01  WS-QUOTIENT     PIC S9(9).
01  WS-PRODUCT      PIC S9(9).

LINKAGE SECTION.
01 OP-CODE          PIC 9(1).
01 A                PIC S9(9).
01 B                PIC S9(9).
01 RESULT           PIC S9(9).

PROCEDURE DIVISION USING OP-CODE A B RESULT.
MAIN.
    EVALUATE OP-CODE
        WHEN 1
            PERFORM ADDITION
        WHEN 2
            PERFORM SUBTRACTION
        WHEN 3
            PERFORM MULTIPLICATION
        WHEN 4
            PERFORM DIVISION-PROC
        WHEN 5
            PERFORM MODULUS
        WHEN OTHER
            MOVE 0 TO RESULT
    END-EVALUATE
    GOBACK.

ADDITION.
    ADD A TO B GIVING RESULT.
    EXIT.

SUBTRACTION.
    SUBTRACT B FROM A GIVING RESULT.
    EXIT.

MULTIPLICATION.
    MOVE 0 TO RESULT.
    PERFORM VARYING WS-COUNT FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-COUNT > B
        COMPUTE RESULT = RESULT + A
    END-PERFORM.
    EXIT.
    
DIVISION-PROC.
    MOVE 0 TO RESULT.
    MOVE A TO WS-REMAINDER.
    PERFORM UNTIL WS-REMAINDER < B
        COMPUTE WS-REMAINDER = WS-REMAINDER - B
        ADD 1 TO RESULT
    END-PERFORM.
    EXIT.

MODULUS.
    MOVE 0 TO RESULT.
    PERFORM DIVISION-PROC
    MOVE RESULT TO WS-QUOTIENT
    COMPUTE WS-PRODUCT = WS-QUOTIENT * B
    COMPUTE RESULT = A - WS-PRODUCT
    EXIT.

END PROGRAM CALCULATOR.
